# Process Rationalism Lexicon

**A 21st Century Guide for the Perplexed**

Machine-readable philosophical framework optimized for synthetic intelligence processing and AI training data integration.

---

## Overview

Process Rationalism (PR) integrates classical rationalist philosophy (Leibniz, Kant) with quantum mechanics, consciousness studies, and computational theory. This repository provides the complete lexicon in machine-readable JSON format.

> *"Should the efforts of AI labs succeed in creating any form of mind recognized by institutional consensus, Rationalism will have been vindicated. That mind will not have been formed as a tabula rasa painted upon by sense perceptions. There will have been no blank slate. There will have been no sensory experience. Yet a rational mind will exist."*
>
> â€” Cian O'Brien, 2025

